enhanced_by.reason: The push method adds an item to the stack, which is necessary to test the pop method.
The peek method checks the top item without removing it, which can be used to verify the state before and after the pop method.
The empty method checks if the stack is empty, which is relevant to test the pop method's behavior when the stack is empty.
The search method can be used to verify the presence of an item before and after the pop method.
